name: Like the Emperor's Robe #9
description:
This is #9 of Like the Emperor's Robe 

The following generative piece appears like the robe of an emperor. When looking closely, you will find that each square is unique as it builds a web of fabric. 

The piece is 2000 x 2000 in order to ensure the ability to display on larger displays.

On Twitter: @generatecoll / Instagram: @generate.collective (2021)
